:A yajddig ut s iẓuṛan
:Ad ur tqqart ula tasust
:Ur a najji yan akk-awin
:Ula nujja-t a kk id-issukf
:A yajddig idln akal
:Ha-yyaɣ d idun ɣ iggi wakal
